WEBVTT

00:03.060 --> 00:05.115
Lay's Stax: Que Rico.

00:05.953 --> 00:08.936
What is the way to a man's heart?

00:09.016 --> 00:11.097
Oh, there are so many ways.

00:11.205 --> 00:14.967
A subtle kiss, a puppy the size of a teacup,...

00:15.207 --> 00:17.272
...a screwdriver with a perfect grip.

00:17.793 --> 00:22.873
But Que Rico believes that the way to a man's heart is through his stomach.

00:23.647 --> 00:26.297
Not every rumble you hear is the gas.

00:27.210 --> 00:29.007
Lay's Stax: Que Rico.

00:29.147 --> 00:31.197
Kick back and crunch.

00:32.118 --> 00:34.979
Sometimes it is a cry for attention.

